<div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p24749273-1.jpg" alt="01。重庆/六公里"><br><span class="pic-title">01。重庆/六公里</span></div><div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p24749273-2.jpg" alt="02。伦敦／塔村  "><br><span class="pic-title">02。伦敦／塔村  </span></div><div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p24749273-3.jpg" alt="03 内罗毕/kibera"><br><span class="pic-title">03 内罗毕/kibera</span></div><div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p24749273-4.jpg" alt="04 Rio/Santa Marta"><br><span class="pic-title">04 Rio/Santa Marta</span></div><div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p24749273-5.jpg" alt="05 istanbul/Halem/Central life"><br><span class="pic-title">05 istanbul/Halem/Central life</span></div><div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p24749273-6.jpg" alt="06 Teheran/Sultan Arbad"><br><span class="pic-title">06 Teheran/Sultan Arbad</span></div><div class="middle"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p24749273-7.jpg" alt="07 Caracas/Petare"><br><span class="pic-title">07 Caracas/Petare</span></div><div class="middle"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p24749273-8.jpg" alt="08 bombay/mulund"><br><span class="pic-title">08 bombay/mulund</span></div><div class="middle"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p24749273-9.jpg" alt="09 Sao Paulo/Jadim Angela"><br><span class="pic-title">09 Sao Paulo/Jadim Angela</span></div><div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p24749273-10.jpg" alt="10 Bangalesh/Karail"><br><span class="pic-title">10 Bangalesh/Karail</span></div>
